    taken from docs/design_system/glyphs.jsx and normalized for WinRT XAML.
    Consumed by buttons and command bars via:

        <Path Data="{StaticResource VgGlyphForward}"
              Stroke="{ThemeResource VgFgBrush}"
              StrokeThickness="1.5"
              StrokeLineJoin="Round"
              StrokeStartLineCap="Round"
              StrokeEndLineCap="Round" />

